ComicInfo.Summary: Bad girls get spanked! But this time it's the college dean who's hungry for discipline from her students, not the other way around! A campus prank at the hands of her sorority sisters sends a college cutie into the arms of this girl-loving cougar who's ready and eager to break out the paddle and dildo, making it the hottest Christmas break ever! Any time of the year is the right time for Teens at Play!
